":"Q_321779010","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":321779010,"title":"为啥现在的课本把hyperbola写成双曲线，而不是拨弨？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/321779010","type":"question","created":1556252196,"answer_count":16,"follower_count":28,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1291,5430,66695,92752,110035],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"Hyperbola旧译为\"双曲线\"，后来严复提出应该翻译成\"拨弨\"。这是一个非常典雅的翻译，与当年江泽涵先生将\"topology\"翻译成\"拓扑学\"有异曲同工之妙。以下是严复先生的原话： 旧译作双曲线…故鄙意终以此译为不可用。按此线如两弓反背，说文止+止是刺止+止也，读若拨。今即以拨字代之，弨反纯弓也，以“拨”字存两字相背之义，以“弨”字象其形，故改今名。 如此美妙的译名，居然被现代课本无视了，不可惜么？"},"attached_info":"Cj4ItaOD08KL9ewuEAMaCDMzNzgyNTI0IKSMiuYFMAA4HEAMcgkzMjE3NzkwMTB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"81 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4dd4bd276016082b1170b87949c8e57e_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"13_1736155276.146904","card_id":"Q_8765713571","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":8765713571,"title":"如何评价 2025 年上海春考英语？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/8765713571","type":"question","created":1736047088,"answer_count":22,"follower_count":34,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[200,1100,134480,1995126,2060863],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAItaOD08KL9ewuEAMaCTExMjcyOTY1MyDw8+e7BjAAOCJADXIKODc2NTcxMzU3MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJv